data.description: Introducing 272 Birch Hollow, a captivating residence in the heart of Florence, New Jersey! Cruise down the charming street, passing by the inviting community clubhouse and pool, until you arrive at your exquisite end-unit townhome. Upon arrival, the expansive driveway, capable of accommodating multiple cars in addition to the garage, catches your attention. Stroll around to the front door and appreciate the enchanting landscaping, complemented by expansive fields just across the street. Step inside, turning left into the warm family room where natural light floods through the windows, highlighting the grand fireplace—a perfect sanctuary for cozy winter days. Transition into the spacious dining room, ideal for hosting memorable dinners, then proceed towards the kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances and stunning cabinetry. Continue into the generous living room, the perfect space for entertaining guests. Journey upstairs to discover the first bedroom, featuring ample closet space. Adjacent, find a full bathroom. Enter the large and exclusive master bedroom, complete with a private full bathroom. Descend downstairs to the rear of the house and step outside to your private patio haven—an idyllic spot for savoring a warm cup of coffee on crisp fall mornings. The location is unparalleled, offering proximity to major highways for easy access to any destination within the state and beyond. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule your private tour today, as 272 Birch Hollow is poised to be off the market soon! Contact us now to experience the charm and convenience of this residence.
